# Copy to .env.local for local dev. Leaving values empty disables analytics
# locally (no network calls), which is the recommended default for development.

# Microsoft Clarity project id (Settings -> Overview in the Clarity dashboard).
# In CI/production this is supplied via the GitHub Actions secret VITE_CLARITY_ID,
# injected by .github/workflows/azure-static-web-apps-gentle-bush-092d4010f.yml.
VITE_CLARITY_ID=
